<c74object name="pnp.sharpness~">

	<digest>
		Calculates the spectral sharpness of an incoming audio signal
	</digest>
	
	<description>
		A sharp sound is one that suggests it might cut if it were to take on physical form. <m>pnp.sharpness~</m> calculates the apparent sharpness of an incoming audio signal by measuring the high frequency content of a sound. The greater the proportion of high frequencies the greater the measure of sharpness will be.
	</description>
	
